Downtown Square~
The Promenade opens here onto the Downtown Square, on the south bank of the
Tokyo River.  All around you is the bustle of Southern Downtown--
shopkeepers on break, a town gossip or two prattling away.  You hear the
river lapping at the pilings of the dock by Kyoko's Sushi, which is to your
north.  8th Avenue begins to the south, the Promenade continues west,
and the concourse ends to your east.
