#3150
Kyoko's Sushi Bar~
This pleasant little place is friendly and bright. The entire place
is made from dark hardwood, and traditional paper. Smells of fresh
fish tantalize your nostrils and a row of cooks stand ready to chop your
order up for you.

Pull up a chair, perhaps play a game, and take time out to talk.
~
